#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn46.130"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.130:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.130:0.2"
msgid "13. Oghavagga "
msgstr "13. Floods "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.130:0.3"
msgid "130. Uddhambhāgiyasutta "
msgstr "130. Higher Fetters "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.137, sc1
msgctxt "sn46.130:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.130:1.2"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, uddhambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are five higher fetters. "

msgctxt "sn46.130:1.3"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "sn46.130:1.4"
msgid "Rūparāgo, arūparāgo, māno, uddhaccaṃ, avijjā—"
msgstr "Desire for rebirth in the realm of luminous form, desire for rebirth in the formless realm, conceit, restlessness, and ignorance. "

msgctxt "sn46.130:1.5"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañcuddhambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni. "
msgstr "These are the five higher fetters. "

msgctxt "sn46.130:1.6"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ uddhambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "The seven awakening factors should be developed for the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these five higher fetters. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.130:1.7"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.130:1.8"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ … "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity, which culminate in the removal of greed, hate, and delusion. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.130:1.9"
msgid "amatogadhaṃ amataparāyanaṃ amatapariyosānaṃ … "
msgstr "“… which culminate, finish, and end in the deathless …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.130:1.10"
msgid "nibbānaninnaṃ nibbānapoṇaṃ nibbānapabbhāraṃ. "
msgstr "“… which culminate, finish, and end in extinguishment … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.130:1.11"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañcannaṃ uddhambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya pahānāya ime satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvetabbā”ti. "
msgstr "The seven awakening factors should be developed for the direct knowledge, complete understanding, finishing, and giving up of these five higher fetters.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.130:1.12"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.130:1.13"
msgid "Oghavaggo terasamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn46.130:2.1"
msgid "Ogho yogo upādānaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.130:2.2"
msgid "Ganthā anusayena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.130:2.3"
msgid "Kāmaguṇā nīvaraṇā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.130:2.4"
msgid "Khandhā oruddhambhāgiyānīti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
